499
00:40:45,470 --> 00:40:49,320
At least the relationship between Prime Minister Gao and the empress now has cracks.

500
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:51,560
We technically didn't miss our target.

501
00:40:51,560 --> 00:40:54,910
Listen up. With Zhao Shixuan's matter,

502
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:58,070
