503
00:40:58,070 --> 00:41:01,640
At the very least, we have to commend the Zhao family for this merit.

504
00:41:01,640 --> 00:41:05,550
Order your men to send some things to the Zhao Manor.

505
00:41:08,100 --> 00:41:11,680
Better send it to Qingluan Hall. Sese will understand what I mean.

506
00:41:16,910 --> 00:41:20,460
My Lord, the empress wishes to see you.

507
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:22,190
What?

508
00:41:23,270 --> 00:41:26,480
If it wasn't for her, Third Younger Brother wouldn't end up like this!

509
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:28,700
She still has the face to come here?

510
00:41:29,990 --> 00:41:33,360
- I don't want to see her.
- Yes, My Lord.

511
00:41:40,660 --> 00:41:44,420
Empress, My Lord is unwell.

512
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:49,180
He is in no condition to meet any guests. It's better that you just go back for now.

513
00:41:50,300 --> 00:41:53,690
